notes:¶

Smaug: the parent cosmological hydrodynamic simulation suite¶

    ID_halo: halo's ID in the Smaug simulation
    Mass_halo: the total mass of halo
    Resolution: the mass of gas particles
    N_halo: the number of dark matter particles within the selected halo
    N0_inbox: the number of dark matter particles within a cube of side equal to twice of the orginal box size. The orignal box is the smallest box which contains all particles belong to the selected halo.

Zing: the zoom-in Smaug suite, resolution improved, N_halo and N0_inbox increased¶

    Time_estimated: the estimated cpu hours
    Storage_estimated: the estimated storage requirment
